title: Dakine Apollo 30L Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2015 Apollo 30L Pack in Black.
Features: 
- Multiple accessory pockets
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 17" laptops
- Padded iPad sleeve
- Top load organizer pockets
- Zippered side pockets
- Quick access pocket
- Adjustable sternum strap
- Side access
- Headphone pocket
